query.content:
## Datakit dashboard

| Datakit Version | Dashboard Date | 
| -------- | -------- |
| 1.65.0     | Dec 20  2024  |

---

This dashboard primarily showing the running status of Datakit. Some metrics are only available in specific versions. Additionally, it is recommended to enable the collection of all Datakit metrics so that these metrics can be showing in the current dashboard:

```toml
# con.d/host/dk.conf
[[inputs.dk]]	
  metric_name_filter = [
    ### Collect all metrics(these may collect 300+ metrics of Datakit)
    ### if you want to collect all, make this rule the first in the list.
    # ".*",   # <-- uncomment this line
```
